        <div xml:id="TK129">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>tīyiṉāṟ cuṭṭapu ṇuḷḷāṟu māṟātē</l>
<l>nāviṉāṟ cuṭṭa vaṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The wound which has been burnt in by fire may heal, but a wound burnt in by the tongue will never heal.</l>
            </lg>
